  <para>Setting this bit to 0 disables the timer output signal, but the timer value accessible from <register_link state="AArch64" id="AArch64-cntps_tval_el1.xml">CNTPS_TVAL_EL1</register_link> continues to count down.</para>
<note><para>Disabling the output signal might be a power-saving option.</para></note>

